criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Over 65 years of age;

          -  Only one participant from each family;

          -  Left-behind for longer than 6 months;

          -  GDS score between 11 and 25.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Psychiatric and medical comorbidities that are potentially life threatening or
             expected to severely limit client participation or adherence;

          -  Those who are currently seeing a cognitive behavioral therapist, psychotherapist or
             counselor;

          -  People unable to understand and fill out the questionnaires.
